devdoc.title: Maintains a sorted list of unsigned ints keyed by address.

contains(SortedLinkedList.List storage,a.notice: Returns whether or not a particular key is present in the sorted list.

getElements(SortedLinkedList.List storag.notice: Gets all elements from the doubly linked list.

getKeys(SortedLinkedList.List storage).notice: Gets all element keys from the doubly linked list.

getValue(SortedLinkedList.List storage,a.notice: Returns the value for a particular key in the sorted list.

headN(SortedLinkedList.List storage,uint.notice: Returns the N greatest elements of the list.

insert(SortedLinkedList.List storage,add.notice: Inserts an element into a doubly linked list.

numElementsGreaterThan(SortedLinkedList..notice: Returns the minimum of `max` and the  number of elements in the list > threshold.

remove(SortedLinkedList.List storage,add.notice: Removes an element from the doubly linked list.

update(SortedLinkedList.List storage,add.notice: Updates an element in the list.
